In [37]:
def dist(pts):
    d = ( np.diff(pts[:,0])**2 + np.diff(pts[:,1])**2 )**.5 *111.12
    d = np.cumsum(d)
    d = np.insert(d, 0, 0)
    return d


def junta_dados(dados, pontos):
    
    x = dist(pontos)
    
    junta = []
    prof = []
    for i, d in enumerate(dados):
        d = d[:-10,:] # elimina o fundo 
        col_dist = np.atleast_2d( np.linspace(x[i], x[i], len(d)) ).T
        prof.append(np.max(d[:,0])) # profundidade máxima do perfil
        d = np.hstack((col_dist, d))
        junta = junta + d.tolist()
        
    junta = np.array(junta)
    prof = np.array(prof)
    # elimina o topo dos perfis
    junta = junta[junta[:,1] > .4]
    
    x2 = [x[-1], x[0], x[0]]
    z2 = [np.max(prof)+2, np.max(prof)+2, prof[0]]
    x2 = np.concatenate((x, x2))
    z2 = np.concatenate((prof, z2))
    mask = np.array([list(row) for row in zip(x2, z2)])
    
    return junta, mask

In [56]:
def interpolador(base, variavel):
    points = base[:,:2]

    xi = np.linspace( np.min(base[:,0]), np.max(base[:,0]), 50)
    yi = np.linspace( np.min(base[:,1]), np.max(base[:,1]), 100)

    xx, yy = np.meshgrid(xi, yi)

    var_i = griddata(points, base[:, variavel], (xx, yy), method='linear')
    
    return xx, yy, var_i

In [58]:
def interp_vars(base):
    variaveis = [2, 3, 9, 10, 11]
    g_var_i = []
    for v in variaveis:
        xx, yy, var_i = interpolador(base, v)
        g_var_i.append(var_i)

    return [xx, yy, g_var_i]

sni = interp_vars(sn)
ssi = interp_vars(ss)
sci = interp_vars(sc)

base = np.copy(sni)
masc = np.copy(mn)

fig = plt.figure(figsize=figsize)

# axis positions
px = .1
py = .8
dx = .8
dy = .18
dint = .02

# colorbar positions
pxcb = px + dx + 0.01
dxcb = 0.01
fc = .02 # to reduce it a little 

axs = []
cbaxs = []
for i in range(5):
    # create the axes
    axs.append(
                fig.add_axes(
                            [px, py-(dy+dint)*i, dx, dy]
                            ))
    cbaxs.append(
                fig.add_axes(
                            [pxcb, py-(dy+dint)*i+fc, dxcb, dy-fc*2]
                            ))
    
    
    cb = axs[i].contourf(base[0], -base[1], base[2][i], cmap='rainbow')
    axs[i].fill(masc[:,0], -masc[:,1], color=[.8, .8, .8])
    
    cbar = plt.colorbar(cb, cax=cbaxs[i])
    cbar.ax.locator_params(nbins=5)
    
    axs[i].set_ylabel('Depth (m)')
    axs[i].text(2, -50, variaveis_l[i])
    axs[i].set_ylim( -np.max(masc[:,1]), 0 )
    if i < 4:
        axs[i].set_xticklabels('')
    if i == 4:
        axs[i].set_xlabel('Distance (km)')
